                FROM `personnel` INNER JOIN `official_productive_units` ON (`official_productive_units`.`RowID`=`personnel`.`Unit_id`)  WHERE `isEnable` =1  LIMIT 0,20

sssssssssssssssqqqqqqqqqlllllll:SELECT p.`RowID`,p.`type`,p.`cDate`,p.`Toward`,p.`Amount`,p.`CashSection`,p.`NonCashSection`,p.`Unit`,p.`desc`,p.`accName`,p.`accBank`,p.`codeTafzili`,p.`nationalCode`,
    p.`paymentMaturityCash`,p.`paymentMaturityCheck`,p.`unCode`,p.`transfer`,p.`payType`,p.`sendType`,p.`consumerUnit`,p.`layer1`,p.`accountID`,p.`layer2`,
    p.`layer3`,p.`totalAmount`,p.`isPaid`,p.`paymentStatus`,ifnull(d.dAmount,0) as dAmount,ifnull(b.check_amount,0) as check_amount,
    (Amount-ifnull(d.dAmount,0)-ifnull(b.check_amount,0)) as remaining FROM  `pay_comment` AS p
    left join (SELECT SUM(dAmount) as dAmount,pid FROM deposit GROUP BY pid) as d on p.RowID=d.pid
    left join (SELECT SUM(check_amount) as check_amount ,cid FROM bank_check GROUP BY cid) as b on p.RowID=b.cid  where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3   AND (Amount-ifnull(d.dAmount,0)-ifnull(b.check_amount,0))>0 ORDER BY p.paymentMaturityCash,p.paymentMaturityCheck Asc LIMIT 0,20
--------------------------------------------------------^^^^----------
--------------------------------------------------------vvvv----------

user id :183
---SELECT 
    COUNT(p.RowID) AS total_count,
    SUM(p.Amount) AS total_amount,
    SUM(p.CashSection) AS total_cash,
    SUM(p.NonCashSection) AS total_check,
    COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0) AS total_dAmount,
    COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0) AS total_check_amount,
    (SUM(p.Amount)-COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0)-COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0)) as total_remining
FROM `pay_comment` AS p
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(dAmount, 0)) AS dAmount, pid 
    FROM deposit 
    GROUP BY pid
) AS d ON p.RowID = d.pid
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(check_amount, 0)) AS check_amount, cid 
    FROM bank_check 
    GROUP BY cid
) AS b ON p.RowID = b.cid where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3  AND   (p.Amount - COALESCE(d.dAmount, 0) - COALESCE(b.check_amount, 0)) > 0
--------------------------------------------------------^^^^----------
--------------------------------------------------------vvvv----------

     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3   AND (Amount-ifnull(d.dAmount,0)-ifnull(b.check_amount,0))>0 ORDER BY p.paymentMaturityCash,p.paymentMaturityCheck Asc LIMIT 0,20

     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3   AND (Amount-ifnull(d.dAmount,0)-ifnull(b.check_amount,0))>0 ORDER BY p.paymentMaturityCash,p.paymentMaturityCheck Asc LIMIT 0,20

     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3   AND (Amount-ifnull(d.dAmount,0)-ifnull(b.check_amount,0))>0 ORDER BY p.paymentMaturityCash,p.paymentMaturityCheck Asc LIMIT 0,20
--------------------------------------------------------^^^^----------
--------------------------------------------------------vvvv----------

user id :183
---SELECT 
    COUNT(p.RowID) AS total_count,
    SUM(p.Amount) AS total_amount,
    SUM(p.CashSection) AS total_cash,
    SUM(p.NonCashSection) AS total_check,
    COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0) AS total_dAmount,
    COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0) AS total_check_amount,
    (SUM(p.Amount)-COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0)-COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0)) as total_remining
FROM `pay_comment` AS p
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(dAmount, 0)) AS dAmount, pid 
    FROM deposit 
    GROUP BY pid
) AS d ON p.RowID = d.pid
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(check_amount, 0)) AS check_amount, cid 
    FROM bank_check 
    GROUP BY cid
) AS b ON p.RowID = b.cid where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3  AND   (p.Amount - COALESCE(d.dAmount, 0) - COALESCE(b.check_amount, 0)) > 0

sssssssssssssssqqqqqqqqqlllllll:SELECT p.`RowID`,p.`type`,p.`cDate`,p.`Toward`,p.`Amount`,p.`CashSection`,p.`NonCashSection`,p.`Unit`,p.`desc`,p.`accName`,p.`accBank`,p.`codeTafzili`,p.`nationalCode`,
    p.`paymentMaturityCash`,p.`paymentMaturityCheck`,p.`unCode`,p.`transfer`,p.`payType`,p.`sendType`,p.`consumerUnit`,p.`layer1`,p.`accountID`,p.`layer2`,
    p.`layer3`,p.`totalAmount`,p.`isPaid`,p.`paymentStatus`,ifnull(d.dAmount,0) as dAmount,ifnull(b.check_amount,0) as check_amount,
    (Amount-ifnull(d.dAmount,0)-ifnull(b.check_amount,0)) as remaining FROM  `pay_comment` AS p
    left join (SELECT SUM(dAmount) as dAmount,pid FROM deposit GROUP BY pid) as d on p.RowID=d.pid
    left join (SELECT SUM(check_amount) as check_amount ,cid FROM bank_check GROUP BY cid) as b on p.RowID=b.cid  where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3   AND (Amount-ifnull(d.dAmount,0)-ifnull(b.check_amount,0))>0 ORDER BY p.paymentMaturityCash,p.paymentMaturityCheck Asc LIMIT 0,20

user id :183
sssssssssssssssqqqqqqqqqlllllll:SELECT p.`RowID`,p.`type`,p.`cDate`,p.`Toward`,p.`Amount`,p.`CashSection`,p.`NonCashSection`,p.`Unit`,p.`desc`,p.`accName`,p.`accBank`,p.`codeTafzili`,p.`nationalCode`,
    p.`paymentMaturityCash`,p.`paymentMaturityCheck`,p.`unCode`,p.`transfer`,p.`payType`,p.`sendType`,p.`consumerUnit`,p.`layer1`,p.`accountID`,p.`layer2`,
    p.`layer3`,p.`totalAmount`,p.`isPaid`,p.`paymentStatus`,ifnull(d.dAmount,0) as dAmount,ifnull(b.check_amount,0) as check_amount,
    (Amount-ifnull(d.dAmount,0)-ifnull(b.check_amount,0)) as remaining FROM  `pay_comment` AS p
    left join (SELECT SUM(dAmount) as dAmount,pid FROM deposit GROUP BY pid) as d on p.RowID=d.pid
    left join (SELECT SUM(check_amount) as check_amount ,cid FROM bank_check GROUP BY cid) as b on p.RowID=b.cid  where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3   AND (Amount-ifnull(d.dAmount,0)-ifnull(b.check_amount,0))>0 ORDER BY p.paymentMaturityCash,p.paymentMaturityCheck Asc LIMIT 0,20
--------------------------------------------------------^^^^----------
--------------------------------------------------------vvvv----------

user id :183
---SELECT 
    COUNT(p.RowID) AS total_count,
    SUM(p.Amount) AS total_amount,
    SUM(p.CashSection) AS total_cash,
    SUM(p.NonCashSection) AS total_check,
    COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0) AS total_dAmount,
    COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0) AS total_check_amount,
    (SUM(p.Amount)-COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0)-COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0)) as total_remining
FROM `pay_comment` AS p
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(dAmount, 0)) AS dAmount, pid 
    FROM deposit 
    GROUP BY pid
) AS d ON p.RowID = d.pid
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(check_amount, 0)) AS check_amount, cid 
    FROM bank_check 
    GROUP BY cid
) AS b ON p.RowID = b.cid where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3  AND   (p.Amount - COALESCE(d.dAmount, 0) - COALESCE(b.check_amount, 0)) > 0
--------------------------------------------------------^^^^----------
--------------------------------------------------------vvvv----------

sssssssssssssssqqqqqqqqqlllllll:SELECT p.`RowID`,p.`type`,p.`cDate`,p.`Toward`,p.`Amount`,p.`CashSection`,p.`NonCashSection`,p.`Unit`,p.`desc`,p.`accName`,p.`accBank`,p.`codeTafzili`,p.`nationalCode`,
    p.`paymentMaturityCash`,p.`paymentMaturityCheck`,p.`unCode`,p.`transfer`,p.`payType`,p.`sendType`,p.`consumerUnit`,p.`layer1`,p.`accountID`,p.`layer2`,
    p.`layer3`,p.`totalAmount`,p.`isPaid`,p.`paymentStatus`,ifnull(d.dAmount,0) as dAmount,ifnull(b.check_amount,0) as check_amount,
    (Amount-ifnull(d.dAmount,0)-ifnull(b.check_amount,0)) as remaining FROM  `pay_comment` AS p
    left join (SELECT SUM(dAmount) as dAmount,pid FROM deposit GROUP BY pid) as d on p.RowID=d.pid
    left join (SELECT SUM(check_amount) as check_amount ,cid FROM bank_check GROUP BY cid) as b on p.RowID=b.cid  where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3   AND (Amount-ifnull(d.dAmount,0)-ifnull(b.check_amount,0))>0 ORDER BY p.paymentMaturityCash,p.paymentMaturityCheck Asc LIMIT 0,20

user id :183
---SELECT 
    COUNT(p.RowID) AS total_count,
    SUM(p.Amount) AS total_amount,
    SUM(p.CashSection) AS total_cash,
    SUM(p.NonCashSection) AS total_check,
    COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0) AS total_dAmount,
    COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0) AS total_check_amount,
    (SUM(p.Amount)-COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0)-COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0)) as total_remining
FROM `pay_comment` AS p
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(dAmount, 0)) AS dAmount, pid 
    FROM deposit 
    GROUP BY pid
) AS d ON p.RowID = d.pid
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(check_amount, 0)) AS check_amount, cid 
    FROM bank_check 
    GROUP BY cid
) AS b ON p.RowID = b.cid where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3  AND   (p.Amount - COALESCE(d.dAmount, 0) - COALESCE(b.check_amount, 0)) > 0

sssssssssssssssqqqqqqqqqlllllll:SELECT p.`RowID`,p.`type`,p.`cDate`,p.`Toward`,p.`Amount`,p.`CashSection`,p.`NonCashSection`,p.`Unit`,p.`desc`,p.`accName`,p.`accBank`,p.`codeTafzili`,p.`nationalCode`,
    p.`paymentMaturityCash`,p.`paymentMaturityCheck`,p.`unCode`,p.`transfer`,p.`payType`,p.`sendType`,p.`consumerUnit`,p.`layer1`,p.`accountID`,p.`layer2`,
    p.`layer3`,p.`totalAmount`,p.`isPaid`,p.`paymentStatus`,ifnull(d.dAmount,0) as dAmount,ifnull(b.check_amount,0) as check_amount,
    (Amount-ifnull(d.dAmount,0)-ifnull(b.check_amount,0)) as remaining FROM  `pay_comment` AS p
    left join (SELECT SUM(dAmount) as dAmount,pid FROM deposit GROUP BY pid) as d on p.RowID=d.pid
    left join (SELECT SUM(check_amount) as check_amount ,cid FROM bank_check GROUP BY cid) as b on p.RowID=b.cid  where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3   AND (Amount-ifnull(d.dAmount,0)-ifnull(b.check_amount,0))>0 ORDER BY p.paymentMaturityCash,p.paymentMaturityCheck Asc LIMIT 0,20

user id :183
---SELECT 
    COUNT(p.RowID) AS total_count,
    SUM(p.Amount) AS total_amount,
    SUM(p.CashSection) AS total_cash,
    SUM(p.NonCashSection) AS total_check,
    COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0) AS total_dAmount,
    COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0) AS total_check_amount,
    (SUM(p.Amount)-COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0)-COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0)) as total_remining
FROM `pay_comment` AS p
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(dAmount, 0)) AS dAmount, pid 
    FROM deposit 
    GROUP BY pid
) AS d ON p.RowID = d.pid
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(check_amount, 0)) AS check_amount, cid 
    FROM bank_check 
    GROUP BY cid
) AS b ON p.RowID = b.cid where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3  AND   (p.Amount - COALESCE(d.dAmount, 0) - COALESCE(b.check_amount, 0)) > 0

     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3  AND   (p.Amount - COALESCE(d.dAmount, 0) - COALESCE(b.check_amount, 0)) > 0

---SELECT 
    COUNT(p.RowID) AS total_count,
    SUM(p.Amount) AS total_amount,
    SUM(p.CashSection) AS total_cash,
    SUM(p.NonCashSection) AS total_check,
    COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0) AS total_dAmount,
    COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0) AS total_check_amount,
    (SUM(p.Amount)-COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0)-COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0)) as total_remining
FROM `pay_comment` AS p
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(dAmount, 0)) AS dAmount, pid 
    FROM deposit 
    GROUP BY pid
) AS d ON p.RowID = d.pid

    FROM bank_check

    (SUM(p.Amount)-COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0)-COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0)) as total_remining
FROM `pay_comment` AS p
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(dAmount, 0)) AS dAmount, pid 
    FROM deposit 
    GROUP BY pid
) AS d ON p.RowID = d.pid
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(check_amount, 0)) AS check_amount, cid 
    FROM bank_check 
    GROUP BY cid
) AS b ON p.RowID = b.cid where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3  AND   (p.Amount - COALESCE(d.dAmount, 0) - COALESCE(b.check_amount, 0)) > 0

    COUNT(p.RowID) AS total_count,
    SUM(p.Amount) AS total_amount,
    SUM(p.CashSection) AS total_cash,
    SUM(p.NonCashSection) AS total_check,
    COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0) AS total_dAmount,
    COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0) AS total_check_amount,
    (SUM(p.Amount)-COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0)-COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0)) as total_remining
FROM `pay_comment` AS p
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(dAmount, 0)) AS dAmount, pid 
    FROM deposit 
    GROUP BY pid
) AS d ON p.RowID = d.pid
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(check_amount, 0)) AS check_amount, cid 
    FROM bank_check 
    GROUP BY cid
) AS b ON p.RowID = b.cid where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3  AND   (p.Amount - COALESCE(d.dAmount, 0) - COALESCE(b.check_amount, 0)) > 0
--------------------------------------------------------^^^^----------
--------------------------------------------------------vvvv----------

    p.`paymentMaturityCash`,p.`paymentMaturityCheck`,p.`unCode`,p.`transfer`,p.`payType`,p.`sendType`,p.`consumerUnit`,p.`layer1`,p.`accountID`,p.`layer2`,
    p.`layer3`,p.`totalAmount`,p.`isPaid`,p.`paymentStatus`,ifnull(d.dAmount,0) as dAmount,ifnull(b.check_amount,0) as check_amount,
    (Amount-ifnull(d.dAmount,0)-ifnull(b.check_amount,0)) as remaining FROM  `pay_comment` AS p
    left join (SELECT SUM(dAmount) as dAmount,pid FROM deposit GROUP BY pid) as d on p.RowID=d.pid

     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3   AND (Amount-ifnull(d.dAmount,0)-ifnull(b.check_amount,0))>0 ORDER BY p.paymentMaturityCash,p.paymentMaturityCheck Asc LIMIT 0,20

    p.`paymentMaturityCash`,p.`paymentMaturityCheck`,p.`unCode`,p.`transfer`,p.`payType`,p.`sendType`,p.`consumerUnit`,p.`layer1`,p.`accountID`,p.`layer2`,
    p.`layer3`,p.`totalAmount`,p.`isPaid`,p.`paymentStatus`,ifnull(d.dAmount,0) as dAmount,ifnull(b.check_amount,0) as check_amount,
    (Amount-ifnull(d.dAmount,0)-ifnull(b.check_amount,0)) as remaining FROM  `pay_comment` AS p
    left join (SELECT SUM(dAmount) as dAmount,pid FROM deposit GROUP BY pid) as d on p.RowID=d.pid
    left join (SELECT SUM(check_amount) as check_amount ,cid FROM bank_check GROUP BY cid) as b on p.RowID=b.cid  where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3   AND (Amount-ifnull(d.dAmount,0)-ifnull(b.check_amount,0))>0 ORDER BY p.paymentMaturityCash,p.paymentMaturityCheck Asc LIMIT 0,20

user id :183
---SELECT 
    COUNT(p.RowID) AS total_count,
    SUM(p.Amount) AS total_amount,
    SUM(p.CashSection) AS total_cash,
    SUM(p.NonCashSection) AS total_check,
    COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0) AS total_dAmount,
    COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0) AS total_check_amount,
    (SUM(p.Amount)-COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0)-COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0)) as total_remining
FROM `pay_comment` AS p
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(dAmount, 0)) AS dAmount, pid 
    FROM deposit 
    GROUP BY pid
) AS d ON p.RowID = d.pid
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(check_amount, 0)) AS check_amount, cid 
    FROM bank_check 
    GROUP BY cid
) AS b ON p.RowID = b.cid where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3  AND   (p.Amount - COALESCE(d.dAmount, 0) - COALESCE(b.check_amount, 0)) > 0

    FROM deposit

) AS d ON p.RowID = d.pid

    FROM bank_check

sssssssssssssssqqqqqqqqqlllllll:SELECT p.`RowID`,p.`type`,p.`cDate`,p.`Toward`,p.`Amount`,p.`CashSection`,p.`NonCashSection`,p.`Unit`,p.`desc`,p.`accName`,p.`accBank`,p.`codeTafzili`,p.`nationalCode`,
    p.`paymentMaturityCash`,p.`paymentMaturityCheck`,p.`unCode`,p.`transfer`,p.`payType`,p.`sendType`,p.`consumerUnit`,p.`layer1`,p.`accountID`,p.`layer2`,
    p.`layer3`,p.`totalAmount`,p.`isPaid`,p.`paymentStatus`,ifnull(d.dAmount,0) as dAmount,ifnull(b.check_amount,0) as check_amount,
    (Amount-ifnull(d.dAmount,0)-ifnull(b.check_amount,0)) as remaining FROM  `pay_comment` AS p
    left join (SELECT SUM(dAmount) as dAmount,pid FROM deposit GROUP BY pid) as d on p.RowID=d.pid
    left join (SELECT SUM(check_amount) as check_amount ,cid FROM bank_check GROUP BY cid) as b on p.RowID=b.cid  where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3   AND (Amount-ifnull(d.dAmount,0)-ifnull(b.check_amount,0))>0 ORDER BY p.paymentMaturityCash,p.paymentMaturityCheck Asc LIMIT 0,20

user id :183
---SELECT 
    COUNT(p.RowID) AS total_count,
    SUM(p.Amount) AS total_amount,
    SUM(p.CashSection) AS total_cash,
    SUM(p.NonCashSection) AS total_check,
    COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0) AS total_dAmount,
    COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0) AS total_check_amount,
    (SUM(p.Amount)-COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0)-COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0)) as total_remining
FROM `pay_comment` AS p
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(dAmount, 0)) AS dAmount, pid 
    FROM deposit 
    GROUP BY pid
) AS d ON p.RowID = d.pid
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(check_amount, 0)) AS check_amount, cid 
    FROM bank_check 
    GROUP BY cid
) AS b ON p.RowID = b.cid where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3  AND   (p.Amount - COALESCE(d.dAmount, 0) - COALESCE(b.check_amount, 0)) > 0

    GROUP BY cid
) AS b ON p.RowID = b.cid where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3  AND   (p.Amount - COALESCE(d.dAmount, 0) - COALESCE(b.check_amount, 0)) > 0

---SELECT 
    COUNT(p.RowID) AS total_count,
    SUM(p.Amount) AS total_amount,
    SUM(p.CashSection) AS total_cash,
    SUM(p.NonCashSection) AS total_check,
    COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0) AS total_dAmount,
    COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0) AS total_check_amount,
    (SUM(p.Amount)-COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0)-COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0)) as total_remining
FROM `pay_comment` AS p
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(dAmount, 0)) AS dAmount, pid 
    FROM deposit 
    GROUP BY pid
) AS d ON p.RowID = d.pid
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(check_amount, 0)) AS check_amount, cid 
    FROM bank_check 
    GROUP BY cid
) AS b ON p.RowID = b.cid where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3  AND   (p.Amount - COALESCE(d.dAmount, 0) - COALESCE(b.check_amount, 0)) > 0

    (SUM(p.Amount)-COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0)-COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0)) as total_remining
FROM `pay_comment` AS p
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(dAmount, 0)) AS dAmount, pid 
    FROM deposit 
    GROUP BY pid
) AS d ON p.RowID = d.pid
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(check_amount, 0)) AS check_amount, cid 
    FROM bank_check 
    GROUP BY cid
) AS b ON p.RowID = b.cid where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3  AND   (p.Amount - COALESCE(d.dAmount, 0) - COALESCE(b.check_amount, 0)) > 0

    COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0) AS total_dAmount,
    COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0) AS total_check_amount,
    (SUM(p.Amount)-COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0)-COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0)) as total_remining
FROM `pay_comment` AS p

    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(dAmount, 0)) AS dAmount, pid 
    FROM deposit 
    GROUP BY pid
) AS d ON p.RowID = d.pid
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(check_amount, 0)) AS check_amount, cid 
    FROM bank_check 
    GROUP BY cid
) AS b ON p.RowID = b.cid where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3  AND   (p.Amount - COALESCE(d.dAmount, 0) - COALESCE(b.check_amount, 0)) > 0

     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3   AND (Amount-ifnull(d.dAmount,0)-ifnull(b.check_amount,0))>0 ORDER BY p.paymentMaturityCash,p.paymentMaturityCheck Asc LIMIT 0,20
--------------------------------------------------------^^^^----------
--------------------------------------------------------vvvv----------

user id :183
---SELECT 
    COUNT(p.RowID) AS total_count,
    SUM(p.Amount) AS total_amount,
    SUM(p.CashSection) AS total_cash,
    SUM(p.NonCashSection) AS total_check,
    COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0) AS total_dAmount,
    COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0) AS total_check_amount,
    (SUM(p.Amount)-COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0)-COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0)) as total_remining
FROM `pay_comment` AS p
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(dAmount, 0)) AS dAmount, pid 
    FROM deposit 
    GROUP BY pid
) AS d ON p.RowID = d.pid
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(check_amount, 0)) AS check_amount, cid 
    FROM bank_check 
    GROUP BY cid
) AS b ON p.RowID = b.cid where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3  AND   (p.Amount - COALESCE(d.dAmount, 0) - COALESCE(b.check_amount, 0)) > 0
--------------------------------------------------------^^^^----------

sssssssssssssssqqqqqqqqqlllllll:SELECT p.`RowID`,p.`type`,p.`cDate`,p.`Toward`,p.`Amount`,p.`CashSection`,p.`NonCashSection`,p.`Unit`,p.`desc`,p.`accName`,p.`accBank`,p.`codeTafzili`,p.`nationalCode`,
    p.`paymentMaturityCash`,p.`paymentMaturityCheck`,p.`unCode`,p.`transfer`,p.`payType`,p.`sendType`,p.`consumerUnit`,p.`layer1`,p.`accountID`,p.`layer2`,
    p.`layer3`,p.`totalAmount`,p.`isPaid`,p.`paymentStatus`,ifnull(d.dAmount,0) as dAmount,ifnull(b.check_amount,0) as check_amount,
    (Amount-ifnull(d.dAmount,0)-ifnull(b.check_amount,0)) as remaining FROM  `pay_comment` AS p
    left join (SELECT SUM(dAmount) as dAmount,pid FROM deposit GROUP BY pid) as d on p.RowID=d.pid
    left join (SELECT SUM(check_amount) as check_amount ,cid FROM bank_check GROUP BY cid) as b on p.RowID=b.cid  where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3   AND (Amount-ifnull(d.dAmount,0)-ifnull(b.check_amount,0))>0 ORDER BY p.paymentMaturityCash,p.paymentMaturityCheck Asc LIMIT 0,20

user id :183
---SELECT 
    COUNT(p.RowID) AS total_count,
    SUM(p.Amount) AS total_amount,
    SUM(p.CashSection) AS total_cash,
    SUM(p.NonCashSection) AS total_check,
    COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0) AS total_dAmount,
    COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0) AS total_check_amount,
    (SUM(p.Amount)-COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0)-COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0)) as total_remining
FROM `pay_comment` AS p
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(dAmount, 0)) AS dAmount, pid 
    FROM deposit 
    GROUP BY pid
) AS d ON p.RowID = d.pid
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(check_amount, 0)) AS check_amount, cid 
    FROM bank_check 
    GROUP BY cid
) AS b ON p.RowID = b.cid where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3  AND   (p.Amount - COALESCE(d.dAmount, 0) - COALESCE(b.check_amount, 0)) > 0

sssssssssssssssqqqqqqqqqlllllll:SELECT p.`RowID`,p.`type`,p.`cDate`,p.`Toward`,p.`Amount`,p.`CashSection`,p.`NonCashSection`,p.`Unit`,p.`desc`,p.`accName`,p.`accBank`,p.`codeTafzili`,p.`nationalCode`,
    p.`paymentMaturityCash`,p.`paymentMaturityCheck`,p.`unCode`,p.`transfer`,p.`payType`,p.`sendType`,p.`consumerUnit`,p.`layer1`,p.`accountID`,p.`layer2`,
    p.`layer3`,p.`totalAmount`,p.`isPaid`,p.`paymentStatus`,ifnull(d.dAmount,0) as dAmount,ifnull(b.check_amount,0) as check_amount,
    (Amount-ifnull(d.dAmount,0)-ifnull(b.check_amount,0)) as remaining FROM  `pay_comment` AS p
    left join (SELECT SUM(dAmount) as dAmount,pid FROM deposit GROUP BY pid) as d on p.RowID=d.pid
    left join (SELECT SUM(check_amount) as check_amount ,cid FROM bank_check GROUP BY cid) as b on p.RowID=b.cid  where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3   AND (Amount-ifnull(d.dAmount,0)-ifnull(b.check_amount,0))>0 ORDER BY p.paymentMaturityCash,p.paymentMaturityCheck Asc LIMIT 0,20

user id :183
---SELECT 
    COUNT(p.RowID) AS total_count,
    SUM(p.Amount) AS total_amount,
    SUM(p.CashSection) AS total_cash,
    SUM(p.NonCashSection) AS total_check,
    COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0) AS total_dAmount,
    COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0) AS total_check_amount,
    (SUM(p.Amount)-COALESCE(SUM(d.dAmount), 0)-COALESCE(SUM(b.check_amount), 0)) as total_remining
FROM `pay_comment` AS p
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(dAmount, 0)) AS dAmount, pid 
    FROM deposit 
    GROUP BY pid
) AS d ON p.RowID = d.pid
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT SUM(COALESCE(check_amount, 0)) AS check_amount, cid 
    FROM bank_check 
    GROUP BY cid
) AS b ON p.RowID = b.cid where
     p.isEnable =1 AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(p.paymentMaturityCash,paymentMaturityCheck) AND  CURRENT_DATE() > IFNULL(paymentMaturityCheck,p.paymentMaturityCash)  AND  p.sendType != 3  AND   (p.Amount - COALESCE(d.dAmount, 0) - COALESCE(b.check_amount, 0)) > 0
--------------------------------------------------------^^^^----------
--------------------------------------------------------vvvv----------
